metadata.name: cabbbage cam :: spiiin portrait
metadata.description:
trial and error is the bread and butter of my practice; it is through this process that most of my ideas are discovered. i wanted to build a camera system that would invite joyful engagement - 'cabbbage cam' is a result of that.


@mathMakesArt said it reminded them of a cabbage cross section, so that's where the name comes from :)
